quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,28,"Ne baboolele mbu amatsi kalakabwa hakari wabu (nende ingamia) mana inyanga yabu yokhunywa amatsi ne iyaga yindi ye ingamia."
  54,29,"Mana nibalaanga omundu wabu, niyetsa mana nayisinza."
  54,30,"Kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje?"
  54,31,"Toto efwe khwabarumila olwang’a lulala lwonyene, nibaba shinga ebitiisi biokhumbashila olukaka."
  54,32,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu khubwitsulisio, ne koo aliwo witsulila?"
  54,33,"Abandu ba Luti bayingasia Abekanyilisi."
  54,34,"Toto efwe khwabarumila eshifulumutu shiamachina, halali abaloondi ba Luti, khwabahabina mumabwibwi."
  54,35,"Tsimbabaasi okhurula khwifwe. Endio nilwa khurunganga ulia ukhupanga orio muno."
  54,36,"Ne toto ye yabekanyilisilia eshinyasio shiefu, halali bo bali netsinganakani khumekanyilisio ako."
  54,37,"Ne toto benya mbu abahelesie abacheni be, mana nikhubawofusia tsimoni tsiabu, nikhubaboolela mbu: “Pile eshinyasio shianje nende amekanyilisio.”"
  54,38,"Ne toto shiabeeshela eshinyasio shitsililila mumabwibi."
  54,39,"Kho mana pile eshinyasio shianje nende amekanyilisio."
  54,40,"Ne toto khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu khubwitsulisio, ne koo aliwo witsulila?"
  54,41,"Ne toto Abekanyilisi betsela Abandu ba Firauni."
  54,42,"Bakhaya ebimanyisio biefu bioosi pe, mana nikhubatila omutilo kwa Wamaani, Wobunyali po."
  54,43,"Ne Abakhayi benyu bali nende amaani okhushila abo baranjilila, nohomba kahandikwa mubitabu mbu enywe mubule okhufunaanibwa tawe?"
  54,44,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “Efwe khuli abaanji khulishila butswa.”"
  54,45,"Abanji abo balashilwa ne balakalukha inyuma tsimbilo."
  54,46,"Halali inyanga yeyindukho niyabalakwa. Ne indukho ni isiro muno mana khandi indulu pa."
  54,47,"Toto Abetsimbi bali mubukori nende mubulalu."
  54,48,"Inyanga yabalikhwesurulwa mafumama khubweni bwabu nibasukunwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu: “Pile omutilo kwomulilo kwa Saqar.”"
  54,49,"Toto efwe buli eshindu khwashiloonga khushichelo shiabura inyuma."